@SIGID.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7001

### ============================================
### AUTH ENDPOINTS - SIGID API
### ============================================

### 1. LOGIN - Authenticate with default admin user
POST {{SIGID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@sigid.com",
    "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### 2. REGISTER - Create a new user
POST {{SIGID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Maria",
    "lastName": "Garcia",
    "email": "maria.garcia@sigid.com",
    "role": "Employed",
    "identificationNumber": "003-1234567-8",
    "password": "Maria123!",
    "confirmPassword": "Maria123!"
}

###

### 3. GET ALL USERS - List all users in the system
GET {{SIGID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. GET USER BY ID - Get a specific user by ID
### Replace {user-id} with an actual user ID
GET {{SIGID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/users/{user-id}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. GET USER BY EMAIL - Get a specific user by email
GET {{SIGID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/users/email/admin@sigid.com
Accept: application/json

###

###
